        <div class="benefit-row">
            <div class="benefit-item"><span class="benefit-txt">초기 매입금 지원</span><span class="benefit-val">20% 즉시지급</span></div>
            <div style="width: 2px; height: 45px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.15);"></div>
            <div class="benefit-item"><span class="benefit-txt">해외선물 수수료</span><span class="benefit-val">$2.0 최저가</span></div>
